---
const today = new Date();
---

<footer>
	<div class="shell footer-inner">
		<p class="footer-title">軌道を描こう。【改】</p>
		<p class="footer-copy">
			PC、制作環境、Web、デジタルカルチャーを扱う個人ブログ。
		</p>
		<p class="footer-meta">&copy; {today.getFullYear()} Stellorbit.net</p>
	</div>
</footer>
<style>
	footer {
		padding: 3.5rem 0 4rem;
		border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
		background:
			radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(176, 106, 67, 0.12), transparent 42%),
			linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(252, 248, 242, 0.7), rgba(252, 248, 242, 0.96));
	}
	.footer-inner {
		text-align: center;
	}
	.footer-title {
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--ink-strong);
		font-weight: 700;
	}
	.footer-copy,
	.footer-meta {
		margin: 0.7rem auto 0;
		color: var(--muted);
		max-width: 42rem;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}
</style>
